{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ８","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记  ８"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着鞭子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勾着胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯着腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一拐的留心着走上山了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口里还大声的喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下你可再也逃不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快乖乖的钻进我的肚子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我好回去安安稳稳的睡大觉。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的声音那么高傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么有自信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但又那么不放心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步，张望一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步，又停一停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远的，他把青草抛到了山坡上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白马就跳上去衔了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到一旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细的嚼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低着颈子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眯着眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象嚼得又香又甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个吓得要死要活的小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是看也不看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管也不管！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他已经到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那黑色的魔手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在推开柴门了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从树枝上飞下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准老山妖的老眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出一根长长的刺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠命的叮了又叮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被叮得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手按着眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪声的大叫大喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我中了原子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定中了原子弹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么一下儿功夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我什么也看不见？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬嗬嗬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我痛得不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的性命完了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜我的好胃口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜我的好江山！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪声怪气的哭起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴着他的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在忍也忍不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就鼓着翅膀扭着腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又唱歌儿又跳舞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗡嗡嗡，嗡嗡嗡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你这个大混蛋送送终。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是你这个小蜂子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害得我以为中了原子弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那太不该！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一向待你并不薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"园子里的花任你采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜂房做好任你住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么忘恩负义倒了戈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反而来叮我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反而来叮我？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你说对我并不薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我辛辛苦苦酿的蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你实在吃得太多多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃得太多多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你赶我的小孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你翻我的窠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我实在再也忍不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这种好意我再也不敢受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向你报仇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向你报仇！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑话，笑话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是大笑话！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂要向我报仇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的事情哪里有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天我再来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带来一把香火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还带来一把鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你喜欢哪一样，让你选一下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子今晚眼睛痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂且饶你再活一夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚一定来吃你的肉，喝你的血。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手按着眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低着头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱着眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸索索的摸下山去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（未完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}